headline.main: U.S. TO REQUISITION EXPORT MATERIALS; Wallace Pushes Survey of Goods Held for Conquered States

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Oct. 9 (AP) -- The Economic Defense Board disclosed today that it intended to requisition large stocks of war materials ordered by countries which later fell under Axis domination.
abstract: Vice Pres Wallace repts Econ Defense Bd will requisition war materials stocks ordered by nations now under Axis domination
